🇲🇽 Mexico 2023! Buck #1

Like last year and since we still have dip 💩 in office the cartels have taken over our ranches we hunted previously. So this year again we hunted a new ranch that one of my coworkers family owns and it didn’t disappoint. 

This was a beautiful ranch and @conner_griner28 was the first one to strike on this beautiful buck. Congrats again Conner! 🍻

🇲🇽 Mexico 2023! Buck #3

@on_the_edge_hunting_  was the next one up and made quick work of this nice Coues! Congrats man I had a blast! Can’t wait to do it again next year. 

Now that we both have AZ early archery bull tags I can’t wait to see what we put down in September! 👍🏻
